      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such amazing care of it, and honestly, it\u2019s in absolutely flawless shape. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. It drives like a total dream and looks even better. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and babied, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
