    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with factory-spec individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. This chassis remains structurally flawless, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term reliability. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Every suspension bushing and damper is factory-spec, maintaining the quintessential M-division handling dynamics. Finished in impeccable original paint with a pristine interior, this example represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
