      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. Finished in a flawless deep metallic paint that has been professionally ceramic coated, the exterior is free of any stone chips, swirls, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin retains its original new-car scent; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This car has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or snow. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a complete, documented service history from the local dealership and a recent comprehensive inspection. The wheels are pristine with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread depth. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is the finest example on the market.",
